characters: Driver of a black sedan, driver of a white car
summary: In this segment, the vehicle is driving on a road with parked cars on both sides. A black sedan on the right side suddenly moves into the lane, causing a collision with a white car on the left side.
actions: The self-driving vehicle maintains a steady speed while observing the black sedan on the right side moving into the lane. The vehicles speed remains consistent until the collision occurs between the black sedan and the white car.
key_objects: 1) Right side: A black sedan, approximately 2 meters away, moving into the lane and causing a collision with the white car. 2) Left side: A white car, approximately 1 meter away, stationary until the collision occurs.
